platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This game absolutely floored us. It seems straightforward at firstyoure a king, and youre presented with choices about how to rule as a deck of cards. Swipe right to choose one path, swipe left for another. But theres so very much more going on, and without spoiling anything, Reigns cleverness, humor, and sometimes agonizing choices routinely surprised and always delighted us.
